Verdcourt (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="817">Taxon</emphasis>
46: 360. 1997) proposed the conservation of the gender of the generic name as masculine. This was recommended by the Committee for Spermatophyta (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="817">Taxon</emphasis>
48: 369. 1999).
</paragraph>
